'''Blaise Compaoré''' (wuxuu dhashay 3 Febraayo [[1951]]) waa siyaasi Burkinabé ah oo madaxweyne ka ahaa [[Burkina Faso]] intii u dhaxeysay 1987 ilaa 2014. Wuxuu si aad ah ugu dhawaa Madaxweyne [[Thomas Sankara]] intii lagu jiray 1980s, iyo Oktoobar 1987, wuxuu hogaamiyay inqilaab xilligii Sankara uu ahaa la dilay. Intaa ka dib, wuxuu soo saaray siyaasad ah "sixitaan", isagoo meesha ka saaray siyaasadihii bidixda iyo siyaasadaha Dunida Saddexaad ee ay daba gashay Sankara. Wuxuu ku guuleystay doorashooyinkii 1991, 1998, 2005, iyo 2010 taas oo loo arkay duruufo aan cadaalad ahayn. Isku daygiisii ahaa inuu wax ka beddelo dastuurka si loo kordhiyo muddadiisa 27-sano ah wuxuu sababay kacdoonkii 2014 Burkinabé. 31 Oktoobar 2014, Compaoré wuu is casilay, halkaas oo uu ugu cararay Ivory Coast.
